Package org.uclab.mm.dcl.llm.monitoring

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MonitoringStrategy
    This is an interface to define the strategy for the monitoring of the activities which may be either physical or nutrition.
    ServiceNotificationChannel
    This is an interface for the service notification channel and have an object of class situation notification.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    LifeLogMonitoring
    This is the main class to start the physical activity monitoring.
    MonitoringContext
    This class provides the contextual information that the various Strategy implementations need.
    NotifyService
    The abstract class for notification management services are defined to give flexibility for communication way.
    NutritionMonitor
    This class is responsible to monitor the nutrition.
    NutritionMonitorTest
    This class is used to define test cases for monitoring the nutrition.
    PhysicalActivityMonitor  
    PhysicalActivityMonitorTest
    This class is used to define test cases for monitoring the physical activities.
    RestServiceNotification
    This class is concrete implementation of ServiceNotificationChannel Interface.
    SCLSituationNotification
    This is the concrete class for the implementation of situation notification.
